The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for 3D face alignment, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which are commonly associated with machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the use of RGB images, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) research.
